Auxiliary_Verbs_key2: Auxiliary verbs ke baare me jaanne ke liye yeh video dekhein.
Auxiliary_Verbs_key4: TO BE, TO HAVE and TO DO are the three primary auxiliary verbs in English.
Auxiliary_Verbs_key5: TO BE has the following forms: Am, is, are, was, were, being, been
Auxiliary_Verbs_key6: TO HAVE has the following forms: Have, has, had, having
Auxiliary_Verbs_key7: TO DO has the following forms: Do, does, did, doing, done
